text: Our Daughter () is a 1981 Cameroonian drama movie directed by Daniel Kamwa (who also starred) and starring Nicole Okala, Stanislas Awona, Elise Atangana, Berthe Mbia, Florence Niasse. It was nominated for the Golden Prize at the Moscow International Film Festival in 1981. == Other websites == * Category:1981 drama movies Category:Cameroonian movies
